text: @UPS phone support (obviously India based) @UPSHelp is useless. How can one box out of two from the same shipment just not show up? #FAIL

@ups @UPSHelp - Yesterday - got message that my package delivery date is today. Changed to pick up at a UPS store not to miss it. Now delivery changed to tomorrow?!?! Why? And your customer support is useless if all it can do is read information I can read online. HELP PLEASE!
@shaisimchi I can understand the frustration. When ever there is a change in delivery, this can cause a 1 to 2 business day delay( depending on the change). ^WS

@UPSHelp Well - it would have been great if this was communicated WHILE I was making the change online. The package is already there...now it just needs to sit there an extra day (a day I can't pick it up...)
@shaisimchi Do you mind providing the tracking number via the link provided? We'd like to provide you more accurate details of what to expect, so this confusion doesn't occur again. ^AP
